Tallahassee.Woman's Working Band House:
Woman's Working Band House is a national historic site located at 648 W. Brevard St., Tallahassee, Florida in Leon County.
It was added to the National Register of Historic Places on October 20, 2010.
This completely restored National Register Property is currently repurposed as a Jazz Club in Tallahassee, Florida: B Sharps Jazz Club.
